flowRoot.flowPara: The one item's remove button is disabled. Removing it would cause the disk to be unable to be unlocked.
It's not possible to add any more top-level slots, so the add button has been disabled.
Slots become "top-level slots". SSS-based "slots" do not have the limited restriction of 8.

"Key group" is a split key. It requires 1 by default, but can be edited to require more. It's possible to add to the key group with the top level +, but this inline + directly adds a new key to this key group (without having to specify).
